  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下Pezkuwi这个缓存基础设施的架构。核心是一个Redis集群，但我想用Etcd来管理配置状态，所以里面要放一个Infra_EtcdCluster节点。另外还需要一个运行时组件Infra_WorkerNode来处理实际任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pezkuwi",
        "PezkuwiNode",
        "PezkuwiRuntime"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Pezkuwi作为外层子图，里面包含Etcd集群和Worker节点。这两个节点之间需要直接连线吗？还是各自独立？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pezkuwi",
        "PezkuwiNode",
        "PezkuwiRuntime"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "先各自独立，不连线。但我想到还有一个外部依赖——FRAME这个框架层需要跟Worker节点有交互，不过不是强依赖，用虚线表示。另外还需要一个SDK组件Infra_IngressController，它要跟Etcd集群有虚线连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRAME",
        "PezkuwiRuntime",
        "PezkuwiSDK",
        "PezkuwiNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Pezkuwi子图画好，包含Etcd和Worker两个节点。然后加上FRAME到Worker的虚线，以及SDK到Etcd的虚线。方向方面，FRAME到Worker是从左到右，SDK到Etcd也是横向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pezkuwi",
        "PezkuwiNode",
        "PezkuwiRuntime",
        "FRAME",
        "PezkuwiSDK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，整体用LR横向布局。SDK放在Pezkuwi子图外面，FRAME也在外面。让我确认一下命名：子图标题用Infra_RedisCache，里面Etcd节点标Infra_EtcdCluster，Worker标Infra_WorkerNode，SDK标Infra_IngressController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pezkuwi",
        "PezkuwiNode",
        "PezkuwiRuntime",
        "PezkuwiSDK",
        "FRAME"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，Pezkuwi子图包含Etcd和Worker，FRAME在左侧用虚线连Worker，SDK在下方用虚线连Etcd。这样架构关系应该清晰了：外部框架通过虚线调度Worker，SDK通过虚线读取Etcd配置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pezkuwi",
        "PezkuwiNode",
        "PezkuwiRuntime",
        "FRAME",
        "PezkuwiSDK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Worker节点的标签我刚才说错了——应该叫PezkuwiRuntime，不是直接叫Infra_WorkerNode。还有Etcd节点是PezkuwiNode，SDK是PezkuwiSDK。子图标题保持Infra_RedisCache。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PezkuwiRuntime",
        "PezkuwiNode",
        "PezkuwiSDK"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
